<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Terms of guarantee;<br>
Payment conditions;<br>
Delivery conditions</strong></p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>Enter the condition texts for ricardo.ch in German and French. The texts will be used in those <strong>listings</strong> for which you have selected the option <strong>According to the description</strong> in the drop-down menus for <strong>Warranty</strong>, <strong>Payment conditions</strong> and <strong>Delivery conditions</strong> in the <a href="/en/omni-channel/multi-channel/ricardo-ch#270"><strong>Listings » Edit listings » Tab: Market</strong></a> menu.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Automatic feedback</strong></p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>Enter up to four feedback texts. These texts will randomly be selected by plentymarkets and used to evaluate the purchaser.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Other</strong></p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>Select <strong>Name 1</strong>, <strong>Name 2</strong> or <strong>Name 3</strong> to determine the item names for listing title and subtitle in the second language. Select <strong>No subtitle</strong> if no subtitle is to be displayed for the ricardo.ch listings.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="700">2.5. Automatically posting feedback</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Set up an <strong><a href="/en/basics/automation/event-procedures">event procedure</a></strong> to automatically send feedback to ricardo.ch.</p>
</div>
<div class="openblock collapseBox">
