</li>
<li>
<p>Enter the SKU.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Add</strong>.<br>
→ The SKU will be saved and displayed.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
<h2 id="800">3. Preparing listings</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Go to <strong>System » Listings</strong> to carry out the settings for all listings regardless of the market. In order to create listings in plentymarkets, you must have carried out the following settings and finished creating your <strong><a href="/en/item">items</a></strong>.</p>
</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="900">3.1. Carrying out the basic settings</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The settings in the <strong>System » Listings » Settings</strong> menu apply to all listings.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Carrying out basic settings for listings:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>System » Listings » Settings</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Pay attention to the explanations given in table 3 and carry out the settings as desired.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<table class="tableblock frame-all grid-all spread">
<caption class="title">Table 3. <strong>Basic settings</strong> for listings</caption>
<colgroup>
<col style="width: 50%;">
<col style="width: 50%;">
</colgroup>
<thead>
<tr>
<th class="tableblock halign-left valign-top">Setting</th>
<th class="tableblock halign-left valign-top">Explanation</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Createing a new market listing</strong></p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>Choose whether an error message should be shown if there is already a listing featuring this item or whether the system should not check for duplicate market listings.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Item name column for the listing title</strong></p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>Select <strong>Name 1</strong>, <strong>Name 2</strong> or <strong>Name 3</strong>. This item name will be transferred. Item names are saved within the item’s <strong><a href="/en/item/managing-items#50">Texts</a></strong> tab.</p>
