<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="1800">3.7. Editing directories</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Rename or delete your subdirectories and directories here.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Editing a directory:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
