<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Stock dependence</strong></p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>Select the <strong><a href="/en/stock-management/managing-stocks#. stock dependence">/en/stock-management/managing-stocks</a></strong> of the listing. Select one of the following options:<br>
<strong>unlimited (with synchronisation)</strong> = The maximum amount that can be purchased will be transferred to the platform. The current stock will not be taken into consideration. Once the stock has been synchronised with plentymarkets, the maximum amount that can be purchased will be offered again on the platform.<br>
<strong>limited (with reservation)</strong> = The current stock from the warehouse will be transferred. If the stock in the warehouse exceeds the maximum amount that can be purchased, then only the amount that is set in the listing will be transferred. The amount will be reserved for the current listing. This amount will not be available for other markets.<br>
<strong>limited (without reservation)</strong> = The current stock from the warehouse will be transferred. If the stock in the warehouse exceeds the maximum amount that can be purchased, then only the amount that is set in the listing will be transferred. The amount will not be reserved for the current listing. The amount will be available for other markets. Overselling can occur if the item is purchased on several different markets at the same time.<br>
<strong>unlimited (without synchronisation)</strong> = The maximum amount that can be purchased will be transferred to the platform. The current stock will not be taken into consideration. Once a purchase is made, the quantity will not be synchronised and will not be refilled. Rather, it will remain as it is.</p>
