<p>It will be faster to use the group function or batch processing depending on the number and type of listings you want to edit. Use <strong>batch processing</strong> with the <strong>Manufacturer</strong> filter if you only want to edit the listings of a certain manufacturer. This way, you can edit all of the listings for one manufacturer without having to select every single listing. Use the <strong>group function</strong> if the listings you wish to edit cannot be grouped with a certain <strong>filter</strong>.</p>
