</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>Select this option to end the listings on markets. Afterwards, the listings will be removed from the active listings. Certain requirements have to be fulfilled in order for listings to be ended. Ask the markets when it is possible to end listings so that you do not violate their conditions.</p>
</div></div></td>
