<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="4500">10.3. Editing active listings with batch processing</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Batch processing includes the same options as the group function. However, the batch processing function edits previously filtered listings. The filters used for narrowing down listings are the same as described for search filters in tables 16 and 18. The procedures are the same as described for group functions in table 19.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Editing active listings with batch processing:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Listings » Batch processing » Active listings</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select the filters. Pay attention to the information given in tables 16 and 18.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Carry out the settings as desired. Pay attention to the information given in table 19.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Execute</strong> to carry out the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
<h2 id="4600">11. Viewing the API log</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The menu <strong>Data exchange » API log » Tab: API log</strong> contains a history of processes that run via the ricardo.ch interface. The <strong>ItemListingControllerRicardo</strong> format is available for ricardo.ch.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Viewing the API log:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Data exchange » API log</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select the <strong>ItemListingControllerRicardo</strong> or <strong>LeaveFeedback</strong> format from the <strong>Process</strong> drop-down menu.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select a date if you only want to see entries for a specific day.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select the number of results per page.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Search</strong> to display the results.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
<h2 id="4700">12. Synchronising data via SOAP API</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Use the SOAP API or the <strong>Data exchange</strong> menu to exchange data between your plentymarkets system and ricardo.ch. The data format <a href="/en/basics/data-exchange/data-formats/itemlistingmarketricardo"><strong>ItemListingMarketRicardo</strong></a> is used to create new ricardo listings or edit existing listings, e.g. to change or delete parameters.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
<h2 id="4800">13. FAQ</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>I tried to list and I received the error messages DeliveryDescriptionMainLanguageIsEmpty, PaymentDescriptionMainLanguageIsEmpty or WarrantyDescriptionMainLanguageIsEmpty. What can I do?</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph indented">
<p><strong>A1</strong>: In the ricardo options, you selected <strong>According to the description</strong> for this listing’s guarantee, payment conditions or delivery conditions. However, you haven’t saved these general conditions yet. To do so, go to <strong>System » Markets » ricardo » Settings</strong> and save the conditions in the submenus <strong>Terms of guarantee</strong>, <strong>Payment conditions</strong> and <strong>Delivery conditions</strong>.[.instruction]
I am unable to select payment methods in the ricardo settings of a listing.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph indented">
<p>Go to <strong>System » Markets » ricardo » Accounts</strong> and update the options for the ricardo markets in the <strong>Update options</strong> area.[.instruction]
My listing was not started or I receive the error message Debited. What could be the problem?</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph indented">
<p>You do not have enough credit on your ricardo account or you have reached your credit limit. Top up your account or apply for a credit limit with ricardo.[.instruction]
I receive the error message TokenErr. What can I do?</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph indented">
<p>Go to <strong>System » Markets » ricardo » Accounts</strong> and update the token.[.instruction]
I receive the error message InvalidPromotion. What is the problem?</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph indented">
<p>One of the additional options is invalid. Check the additional options that were selected.[.instruction]
I receive the error message UnknownCategoryId. What is the problem?</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph indented">
<p>No category was specified or the specified category is invalid.</p>
</div>
</div>
